<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q9_v10" title="Q9_v10" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Un taxi cobra $900 por cada kilómetro recorrido dentro de la ciudad, $1200 por cada kilómetro en carretera y $150 por cada minuto de espera. En un recorrido, una pasajera viaja 3,5 km en la ciudad, 7,2 km en carretera y el taxi espera 4,5 minutos antes de continuar el viaje.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4200</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6480</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6480</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;355</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero el viaje descrito se representa con ciudad a $900 por km y carretera a $1200 por km, no al revés.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Esta expresión usa exactamente las tarifas del enunciado: ciudad <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3150</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, carretera <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8640</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y espera <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces el costo total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8640</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;465</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión suma primero los kilómetros <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10,7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y luego cobra todos a $900 por km: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>10,7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9630</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. La espera vale <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En total da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9630</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10&#160;305</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero los 7,2 km en carretera deben cobrarse a $1200 por km.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>$</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Los dos primeros términos sí corresponden al viaje: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3150</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8640</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero la espera debe cobrarse a $150 por minuto, no a $1200. Esta opción calcula <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>5400</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y por eso obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8640</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>5400</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>17&#160;190</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que no representa el cobro descrito.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="FB_NoResponse" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p>No se registró una alternativa válida. Revisa las tarifas del enunciado y selecciona una opción.</p>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar qué se cobra en cada parte del viaje</strong></p>
            <p>Dentro de la ciudad se cobran $900 por kilómetro, en carretera se cobran $1200 por kilómetro y la espera se cobra a $150 por minuto.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el costo del trayecto en ciudad</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3150</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>El costo en ciudad es $3 150.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular el costo del trayecto en carretera</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8640</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>El costo en carretera es $8 640.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular el costo de la espera</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>El costo de la espera es $675.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Sumar los tres cobros</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3150</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>8640</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>675</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;465</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>7,2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4,5</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, que corresponde a la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_NoResponse</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>